29720,An entire city in the deathly grip of a gang of invisible criminals'", 2295,"A wave of bank robberies has police stumped as no one has seen the crooks. Dr. Frost stumbles upon Professor Gunther a scientist who has invented a ray gun which turns people temporarily invisible. He learns that Gunther's assistant Lehr has stolen the gun to turn commit the crimes. Frost must turn invisible himself to catch the villains.",NULL,NULL,19
